PROJECT.NAME: inOsmFulv5-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Osmylus fulvicephalus, mitochondrial assembly, inOsmFulv5-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides the mitochondrial assembly of Osmylus fulvicephalus. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
